It's an interesting-- I think
a lot of these self-help things

00:48:11.420 --> 00:48:13.640
that I did, there were one
or two points within them

00:48:13.640 --> 00:48:15.350
that were interesting and
that I took away and thought

00:48:15.350 --> 00:48:16.490
about some more.

00:48:16.490 --> 00:48:18.470
And there were things
in the Landmark forum,

00:48:18.470 --> 00:48:20.390
there were things
from mindfulness

00:48:20.390 --> 00:48:23.420
that I think in certain
situations can be useful.

00:48:23.420 --> 00:48:26.360
But I think, overall, any
one package of solutions,

00:48:26.360 --> 00:48:30.920
I think is usually
over-promising quite heavily.

00:48:30.920 --> 00:48:35.350
And so there was no one
brick or apple, course,

00:48:35.350 --> 00:48:38.520
